            "text": "Lebam River Kayaking Adventure from Desaru , Johor"
          }
        ]
      },
      "description": {
        "localized_texts": [
          {
            "language_code": "en",
            "text": "Enjoy a scenic pick-up from your hotel within the Desaru Coast area followed by a comfortable 15-minute drive to the tranquil Lebam River. Upon arrival, you will board a local transfer boat that transports you and the kayaks upstream to the quieter upper section of the river where the adventure begins. Once on the water, paddle gently through calm mangrove-lined channels surrounded by lush greenery, where you may spot wild ducks, herons, and colorful kingfishers that thrive within this serene ecosystem.After approximately 90 minutes of kayaking, you will meet the safety boat for the return journey back to Kuala Sungai Lebam. Before heading back to your hotel, the tour includes a stop at the popular Desaru Fruit Farm Shop, where you can browse and purchase locally harvested fresh fruits. The experience concludes with a relaxed drive back to your accommodation in Desaru Coast, offering a perfect blend of active exploration and natural beauty."
          }
        ]
      },
